trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameCollection class is a read-only collection of service principal names.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ServiceNameCollection er en skrivebeskyttet samling av tjenesten UPN-navnene.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameCollection class is used in an <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ExtendedProtectionPolicy> when validating against a custom list of service provider names (SPNs).
trans-unit.target: Klassen ServiceNameCollection er brukt i en <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ExtendedProtectionPolicy>Når du validerer mot en egendefinert liste over tjenesten Leverandørnavn (SPNer).</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.ExtendedProtectionPolicy>
